        "book_cover":"/assets/images/bookpics/innovators_dilemma.jpg",
        "description": "This book is about how businesses get disrupted even though there are big competitors that could just wipe them clean. A Wall Street Journal and Businessweek bestseller. Named by Fast Company as one of the most influential leadership books in its Leadership Hall of Fame. An innovation classic. From Steve Jobs to Jeff Bezos, Clay Christensen’s work continues to underpin today’s most innovative leaders and organizations.",
